name: AND
body:
### AND.
AND is another name daemon, or an Apache-licensed Named Daemon, or something else.

It's a progression from the thoughts I had when failing to write [R Squared](http://rsquared.io)

Today is the 12th August 2014. I wonder how long it will take before any code lands.
